Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.90,0:24:49.40,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露天風呂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.00,0:24:51.20,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘湯雪闇？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.20,0:24:52.10,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振袖事件？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.10,0:24:54.00,jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,やっぱり意味わからん…
